title: Project Runway All Stars S03E04 Keepin It Classy WEB-DL
description:
Keepin' It Classy

ReleasedNov 14, 2013

It's back to school for the remaining eight designers in this fan-favorite unconventional challenge to create high impact fashion from materials found in an elementary school classroom. Guest judges are actors Michael Urie and Gabourey Sidibe.

Accept no retagged cheap Pakki substitutes,thanks to RKSTR for the real thing
